He re’s How Tanmay Bhatt Lost More Than 110 KGs Swagata Dam Feb . 23 . 2017 Tanmay Bhat 
Popular stand-up comedian Tanmay Bhatt is more than 110 kilos lighter and is looking fitter than ever. The one who helped him drop these pounds is Ranveer Allahbadia – a fitness Youtuber. He took to Instagram to share how he helped Tanmay in his weight loss journey. Check out his post. A post shared by Ranveer Allahbadia (@beerbiceps) on Feb 16, 2017 at 6:08am PST 
Now, that’s some major #FitInspiration! 0
